WorkItem.Description: We have CSV data that we convert to Excel with PHPExcel that has equal signs as the first character. However, it's not actual formula data, so we get "Formula Error" Exceptions when attempting to use "loadIntoExisting". We would like the option to use "setValueExplicit" instead of "setValue" when loading data, so that we can load this data without issue.
WorkItem.Summary: Option to Use setValueExplicit in CSV Reader
